ow\" >click here to contact us</a>.</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"sticky\">Sponsored Sticky Posts</h4>\n<p>Sponsored sticky posts are affordable upgrades to increase\u00a0your posts&#8217; visibility, pushing your ad near the top of the list and attracting more replies (and potentially clients). Only the homepage and city\u00a0categories display sponsored sticky posts and are capped at 5 spots per city, per week (1 city, 7 days).</p>\n<p><strong>City Category</strong> &#8211; R100 per week*<br />\n<strong>Homepage Add-on</strong>\u00a0&#8211; R150 per week**</p>\n<h4>BUY YOUR SPONSORED STICKY POST</h4>\n<p>Follow these <strong>3 easy steps</strong> to have your sponsored sticky post <strong>activated quickly</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">1. Start by creating / finishing up your post.<br />\n2. Come back here and fill in the form below.<br />\n3. Make payment with the correct reference.</p>\n<p>And that&#8217;s it.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"/contact\" target=\"_blank\"  rel=\"nofollow\" >If you need any assistance, we&#8217;re here to help <img src=\"http://escortforum.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png\" alt=\":)\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></a></strong></p>\n<div class=\"sponsored-sticky-form\">\n<p><em>All fields are required.</em></p>\n<div role=\"form\" class=\"wpcf7\" id=\"wpcf7-f102-p35-o1\" lang=\"en-ZA\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"></div>\n<form action=\"/advertising/#wpcf7-f102-p35-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form\" novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"102\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"4.4.2\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"en_ZA\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f102-p35-o1\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpnonce\" value=\"39022679c0\" />\n</div>\n<p><strong>What is your name?</strong> <br /><em>(Or username)</em><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-name\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"your-name\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-validates-as-required\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </p>\n<p><strong>What is your email address?</strong> <br /><em>(For this account)</em><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-email\"><input type=\"email\" name=\"your-email\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-email wpcf7-validates-as-required wpcf7-validates-as-email\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </p>\n<p><strong>What is your contact number?</strong> <br /><em>(Whatsapp numbers welcome)</em><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-tel\"><input type=\"tel\" name=\"your-tel\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-tel wpcf7-validates-as-required wpcf7-validates-as-tel\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /></span> </p>\n<p><strong>Choose Your Sticky Position Options</strong><br /> <em>(Amounts are per week and total)</em><br />\n<span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap sticky-options\"><span class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-radio\"><span class=\"wpcf7-list-item first\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"sticky-options\" value=\"City - R100\" checked=\"checked\" />&nbsp;<span class=\"wpcf7-list-item-label\">City - R100</span></span><span class=\"wpcf7-list-item last\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"sticky-options\" value=\"City + Homepage - R250\" />&nbsp;<span class=\"wpcf7-list-item-label\">City + Homepage - R250</span></span></span></span>\n    </p>\n<p><strong>Anything else you would like to tell us or know?</strong><br />\n    <span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-message\"><textarea name=\"your-message\" cols=\"40\" rows=\"10\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-textarea\" aria-invalid=\"false\"></textarea></span> </p>\n<p><input type=\"submit\" value=\"BUY SPONSORED STICKY POST\" class