authorized access and we offer the use of a secure socket layer (SSL). A secure socket layer is used to assist in the encryption of information. (You may be able to discern whether your information is being transmitted via SSL by making certain that the Uniform Resource Locator (URL) is prefixed with \u201chttps\u201d rather than \u201chttp\u201d and that a padlock icon is displayed on the lower right corner of your browser (for transmissions via MS Internet Explorer)). If you make a payment through this site, you may be directed to a third party site for payment processing or verification; the policies of such third party site may apply to the processing of your transaction. We are not responsible for the policies of any third party sites.</p>\n<h4>Forum Profile Updates</h4>\n<p>If you are a member and have registered with us, we encourage you to update your information as\u00a0it changes. We welcome your updates, questions and comments. Please send e-mails to\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:escortforum@bigblackbook.co.za\" target=\"_blank\"  rel=\"nofollow\" >escortforum@bigblackbook.co.za</a>\u00a0and we will promptly respond to your requests.</p>\n<h4>Privacy Changes</h4>\n<p>Whenever we change our privacy policy, we will make reasonable commercial efforts to promptly post a notice on this site indicating that new information has been posted. If at any point we decide to use personally identifiable information in a manner different from that stated at the time it was collected, we will take reasonable commercial efforts to promptly notify you by way of email. To the extent practicable, we will endeavor to offer you a choice as to whether or not we use information previously collected in a different manner. We will take reasonable commercial efforts to use information in accordance with the privacy policy under which the information was collected.</p>\n<h4>Required Disclosure of Information</h4>\n<p>Though we make every effort to preserve your privacy, we may disclose your